		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The scrolling issue for example could be handled with pattern blanking on the topmost and bottommost scanlines (à la Jurassic Park, relatively simple if you're using the MMC3) and a scrolling engine that doesn't require the screen to be vertically aligned with the name tables (i.e. an 8-way engine).

		

		</td>
